### Me (로그인 확인)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Games - List (내 게임 목록)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me/games?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 기본
GET http://localhost:4000/api/me/games?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 기간
GET http://localhost:4000/api/me/games?from=2025-12-01&to=2025-12-31&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Stats
GET http://localhost:4000/api/me/stats?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

GET http://localhost:4000/api/me/stats?from=2025-10-01&to=2025-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### (5) List Games (최근 20개)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me/games?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### (6) List Games (기간 from/to)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me/games?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-01-31&limit=200
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### (4) Create Game
# @name createGame
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/me/games
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "score": 25,
  "inning": 35,
  "result": "WIN",
  "gameType": "1v1",
  "gameDate": "2026-01-20",
  "memo": "REST Client로 생성"
}

### (7) Get One Game
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me/games/6976f84df8040bc4501559bc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### (8) Update Game (PATCH 형태로 일부만)
PATCH  {{baseUrl}}/api/me/games/{{gameId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "score": 30,
  "memo": "점수/메모 수정"
}


### (9) Delete Game
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/me/games/{{gameId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### (10) Stats - all
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me/stats?mode=all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### (11) Stats - recent limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me/stats?mode=limit&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### (12) Stats - range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me/stats?mode=range&from=2026-01-01&to=2026-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### me insights - recent 20 (default)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/me/insights
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### me insights - recent 10
GET http://localhost:4000/api/me/insights?mode=limit&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### me insights - range
GET http://localhost:4000/api/me/insights?mode=range&from=2026-01-01&to=2026-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### me insights - all
GET http://localhost:4000/api/me/insights?mode=all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### (1) 이번달 랭킹 - AVG 기준 (기본값)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ranking
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### (2) 이번달 랭킹 - AVG 기준 (명시)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ranking?mode=thisMonth&metric=avg&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### (3) 이번달 랭킹 - WINRATE 기준
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ranking?mode=thisMonth&metric=winRate&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### (4) 전체 랭킹 - AVG 기준
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ranking?mode=all&metric=avg&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### (5) 전체 랭킹 - WINRATE 기준
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ranking?mode=all&metric=winRate&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### (6) 잘못된 파라미터 테스트(400 기대)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ranking?mode=foo&metric=bar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

